imdb.plot outline: Have Gun Will Travel follows the adventures of our two enigmatic co-stars as they interact with all facets of the modern day world of shooting, hunting and all the accoutrements that go with this exciting, emerging industry worldwide. Its an exciting romp into the world where nature meets man...and apparently very independent women.
imdb.title: Have Gun Will Travel Television Show
